        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Day 4 - Highlands & Ramen"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We spent our entire fourth day on a tour of the Scottish Highlands. It was breathtaking and so worth the time. My "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/2016/02/travel-with-me-adventure-in-the-scottish-highlands/",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "next post"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " will be about that tour, so I'll save the pictures for now."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "When we arrived back from the tour around 7pm, we were starving. We ended up eating dinner at a delicious ramen place called "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "strong"
              }
            ],
            "text": "Hakataya"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ". Since our apartment in Austin is right across the street from "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://ramen-tatsuya.com/",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "the best ramen place in the world"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", I was skeptical. But it ended up being delicious! I recommend it for a cold night in Edinburgh. Nothing like a hot bowl of noodles and broth to warm you up!"
          }
        ]
      },
